  m_Text: Now that everything is set up, you can send those localization text files
    to AI for translation. Additionally, players can contribute to localization by
    modifying the existing text files or creating their own and placing them into
    the same folder. The system will automatically read all the text files in that
    folder and use the file names as the Language Name options.
